long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Smart Links GPT saves HOURS by predicting which links you will click, and loading the page– before you can click!

The science –
It takes on average 350ms to mouse-over and click a link. (install and take our test to see your time) 

Research shows that after pausing just 50ms over a link, there is a one-in-two chance that you will click it. Smart Links GPT uses an AI prediction algorithm to start loading the page at the earliest moment – giving you a huge head start. So before you can click, the page is already loaded and appears almost instantly.

Works on ALL websites

Smart Links GPT is still in BETA so if you experience any bugs, just email us and we'll try our best to help you resolve the issue!
